precis:
Order authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a CONVENTION
between Canada and JORDAN for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION and the
PREVENTION of FISCAL EVASION with respect to TAXES ON INCOME (with
